These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, canadian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, train
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the canadian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | canadian    | turkish |
| Sport         | sailing | handball    |
| Transport     | airplane     | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, french
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the malaysian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | cola  | coffee   |
| Nationality   | french | malaysian  |
| Transport     | quad-bike   | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, board-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, action
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | board-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | action | comedy  |
| Sport         | rugby   | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
