The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, subway
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | lettuce | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | adventure   |
| Transport     | subway       | helicopter      |

