.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, peas
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, manager
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the pilot##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
3. the person eating onion is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | peas | onion     |
| Job     | manager | pilot |
| Sport   | lacrosse | climbing    |

 #################################

 
