.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, puzzles
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, french
2 different pets are kept: mouse, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the russian is on the left of the french##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | puzzles | chess |
| Nationality   | russian     | french     |
| Pet           | horse          | mouse     |

