.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, helicopter
1. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | sports |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | salsa  |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus    |

 